sources.description:
The Supercops: Nobody's Safe On Either Side of the Law!
An attempted robbery turns to be an unexpected recruitment when two unemployed men mistakenly break into a police office instead of a store.

Original title: I due superpiedi quasi piatti
AKA: Two Supercops / Trinity: In Trouble Again

Director & Writer: Enzo Barboni
Stars: Terence Hill, Bud Spencer, David Huddleston
Genres: Action, Comedy, Adventure, Crime
